          </div>
          <h1 class="title" id="page-title" itemprop="name headline alternativeHeadline">Why My Hectic Morning Routine Rules (and I&#039;m Not Changing It)</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="top-share">
          <div class="group_share" data-recirc-section>
  <div class="share-buttons icons" data-origin="top">
    <div ng-controller="socialCtrl"
